## mb-framework workflow

This project uses [mb-framework](https://github.com/Yanick-mj/mb-framework).
Stage-aware, markdown-only, CLI-only agent pipeline.

**Core commands:**

| Command | When to use |
|---|---|
| `/mb:validate "idea"` | Validate a new idea before coding (stage=discovery) |
| `/mb:ship "wedge"` | Ship a janky MVP wedge in <48h (stage=mvp) |
| `/mb:feature "description"` | Normal feature work (stage=pmf+) |
| `/mb:fix "bug"` | Bug fix flow |
| `/mb:review` | Code review current changes |
| `/mb:backlog` | Priority-sorted backlog of stories |
| `/mb:roadmap` | Strategic roadmap |
| `/mb:tree [STU-X]` | Story hierarchy tree |
| `/mb:deliverables STU-X` | Typed versioned artifacts per story |
| `/mb:runs [N]` | Last N agent runs |
| `/mb:stage` | Current stage + upgrade criteria |

## Files to know

| Path | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `mb-stage.yaml` | Current stage (discovery/mvp/pmf/scale) + upgrade criteria |
| `_roadmap.md` | Strategic roadmap for this project |
| `_backlog/*.md` | Stories not yet scheduled — priority-sorted in `/mb:backlog` |
| `_bmad-output/deliverables/<story>/` | Typed versioned artifacts (PLAN/IMPL/REVIEW/DOC) |
| `_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/stories/` | Active stories (in_progress, in_review) |
| `memory/` | Persistent project state (codebase-index, cost-log, runs log) |
| `memory/_session/` | Ephemeral handoff between agents in one session |

